Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼她要盯著我們看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們只是旅行 又沒做壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為那是她的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.66,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後就鬧大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.87,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後呢 之後怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飛機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們就是要搭這架飛機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的要搭飛機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我經常夢到自己是飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飛機？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就是飛機
