Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飛機已進入平穩飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燈熄了表示乘客可以離開座位走動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靜不下心來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真沒想到報瀨也是第一次搭飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然為媽媽送行過很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但沒有實際搭過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小結搭過很多次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是因為工作的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個要怎麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上面有個遊戲的圖示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要點這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是蕎麥麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能用芹菜換你的雞蛋燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}綠茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}右轉 往右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你別擠到我這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 為什麼只有我沒得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你在睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把這裡的「數據漫遊」關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把她叫醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虧你還睡得著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 全是英語耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們要走哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要坐地鐵就走MRT的方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs30\pos(690,650)}城市快捷運輸系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼會忘記兌換貨幣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且怎麼把身上的錢都換了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們後天早上就要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不提前跟我說 我會忘嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夏天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟我們在赤道附近嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上次來的時候 我也有點想死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魚尾獅呢 魚尾獅！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好怪的建築
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給點優惠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}優惠！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等會再來買啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是來個飯店就花這麼多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰叫你們買那些東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是為了轉機去費利曼圖才下機的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我們就待一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能隨意行動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雙人床
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}預備 1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先出石頭 剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}決定誰睡在小理身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理 你能睡在地上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正睡床上也會滾下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你訓練時就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我完全沒印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這才是問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出門前 先把貴重物品放進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日元 機票 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都在自己房間準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}30分鐘後在大廳集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我見過那個 是個泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:07.93,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※新加坡濱海灣金沙酒店，55層的泳池冠絕世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有想像中那麼讓人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 我聽說很讓人失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們居然想失望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}排好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}擺什麼姿勢 擺什麼姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是烏龍茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}菜單上是這麼寫沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}味噌拉麵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都說沒有那東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但這是拉麵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為沒有味噌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這沒搞錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃不下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 你嘴巴沒合上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我買到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}榴槤冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你居然還吃得下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是甜點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向要不要嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得我會吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就給報瀨吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我早說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小結
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}入境檢查時要出示護照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那當然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還帶在身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然 就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泳池呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那邊 但只有這裡的住客才能進去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是個普通的泳池 就是景色很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧 你進去過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前有次進去拍過照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道說是性感泳裝寫真模特兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在笑話我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡有點像海上的十字路口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人們來到這裡 還會再前往世界各地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}厲害什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}後天 我們從這裡出發之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡的風景還會是這個樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管我們是去南極 還是回到日本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡每天還是會有船靠港
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}城裡還是會有許多人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上學 上班 和朋友們玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每個人都繼續平時的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這話放到日本也適用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}學校今天依然有開課
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在大概吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:10:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我們沒有見過 也不了解的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也有許許多多的人過著各式各樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每天每天 從不間斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然都是理所當然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過我能懂這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你隱瞞了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隱瞞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說不定會自己冒出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但也不可能找成這樣都找不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這麼說也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有護照的話 別說出國了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}連日本都回不去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎 如果它一直不出來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦 我以前住在日本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼到了這裡還在便利商店上班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}後天就要飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會有辦法 總會有辦法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼辦法？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}辦法嘛…你想 肯定有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這…吐槽得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之先查查看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果遺失護照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要到大使館重新辦理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最快也得花半天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天去還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是大使館星期日和節日沒開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}星期日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}憑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明我們便利商店員 可是24小時全年無休
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這群臭公務員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能換搭晚兩三天的班機了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然到的時間會有點晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過還是能趕上發船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天去機場服務處問一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要改…抵達日期嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有這個辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想 觀測隊在紀律上是很嚴格的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會告訴我們不用來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會啦 事出有因嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傳個郵件問問佳苗小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要傳郵件說會遲到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得這樣做比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是後天早上才走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有整整一天 明天再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也許它會自己突然出現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請你快快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.50,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魚尾獅…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真想殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之 你們三個後天先去澳大利亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一個人也會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等趕上了 就會追上你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是沒趕上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不就是回日本嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}機票錢還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會去跟真理她們說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是我說不想變日期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我心裡也清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為不能按計劃走 心裡會有些煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弄丟護照的人是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該道歉的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事實就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想給大家添麻煩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是真像你說的 都去不了南極怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就追悔莫及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我又沒有說不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是讓你們三個人先走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會追上去的 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 就這樣定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是四個人一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天跟佳苗小姐發郵件說明一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想洗個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明你這麼為我著想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我對這種事一直應付不來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然明白這種事其實很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我只要被別人關心就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該說是鬧彆扭呢 還是說看不透別人的本意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以連高中都不想上 想儘可能獨來獨往
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結果我跟什麼人在一起 都會有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以你不用在意 全都是我自己的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會的 我也有自己的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上高中後就一直全力釋放著別靠近我的氣場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不擅長與人相處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:20.00,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你現在就是在關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說了 我不喜歡被別人關心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨比任何人都想去南極吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把這點作為首要目標去考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣一來 我也會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鬧鐘沒響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這邊 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們怎麼自己跑出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我聽說你是身體不適才睡覺的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月去問機票能不能改了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這件事就不用你們操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經說好了 你們三個先去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒聽過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那之後已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別講傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼那麼意氣用事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是誰意氣用事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種票要一個多月後才有位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為本來就是特價機票
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看 我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之你們三個明天先去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一個人去補辦護照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改簽！推延兩天！機票！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs30\pos(640,650)}Change, later two days, air
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100萬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想改簽！四個人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs30\pos(640,650)}Please change, four person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 為什麼要意氣用事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}意氣用事有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}固執 被人取笑 鬧得不高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我依然很意氣用事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我沒有做錯什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你不想我關心 就直說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不想當 別人說不用關心 就真不關心的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不想當 別人叫他先走 就真走了的無情的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說好四個人一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不想當出爾反爾的窩囊廢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們四個人一起走 這就是首要目標！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我覺得不是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是商務艙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用做到這種地步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有別的空位 也只能這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弄丟就麻煩了 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是100萬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在得意些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有得意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 也有點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是怎樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不喜歡被別人擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就不用擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之現在得四個人一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天大家一起去大使館…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鞋帶鬆了 幫我拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不找個地方裝 很容易掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海南雞飯 海南雞飯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 海南雞飯和咖椰烤吐司來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 哇 看起來真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你隱瞞了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隱瞞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩位趕快開動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨和日向的榴槤秀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的要吃這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就放過你們了 還不快感謝我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是 你知道我們多擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是商務艙票也退票了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出發日還是明天不變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還剛好分成了四塊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}猜拳輸的一方吃如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這哪裡算什麼水果之王了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過習慣了 可能還挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的
Comment: 0,0:21:59.00,0:21:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:19.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}長いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:30.74,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:36.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}間違っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:47.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:58.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}汚れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:09.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言葉も　きっと見つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:14.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:20.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:19.81,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}尋找著漫長隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:30.74,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光氣味的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:36.37,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走錯了 也別忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:47.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:58.06,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}緊緊捏住手心裡 髒髒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:09.36,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}沒說出口的話 我也一定會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:14.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}隨你們嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:20.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 邁出腳步
